fields.name: Active
fields.description: The user has normal access to their account and can perform operations without restrictions.

fields.name: Blocked
fields.description: The user has attempted to access their account with incorrect credentials multiple times and has been temporarily blocked to prevent brute-force attacks.

fields.name: Disabled
fields.description: The user has requested to disable their account or has violated the bank's terms and conditions, resulting in their access being revoked.

fields.name: Pending Verification
fields.description: The user has created a new account and needs to verify their identity or provide additional information to activate their account.

fields.name: Verified
fields.description: The user has completed the verification process and their account is active.

fields.name: Suspended
fields.description: The user has violated the bank's security policies or has performed suspicious activities, resulting in their account being temporarily suspended.

fields.name: Cancelled
fields.description: The user has requested to cancel their account and no longer has access to it.

fields.name: Inactive
fields.description: The user has not accessed their account for an extended period of time and their account has been marked as inactive.

fields.name: Under Review
fields.description: The user has made a password change request or has updated their personal information, and their account is under review to verify the authenticity of the request.

fields.name: Lockout
fields.description: The user has attempted to access their account with incorrect credentials multiple times and has been permanently blocked to protect their account from malicious attacks.

fields.name: Retail customers
fields.description: An individual user who has a personal account at the bank and performs basic banking operations, such as deposits, withdrawals, and transfers.

fields.name: Business customers
fields.description: A company or organization that has a commercial account at the bank and performs more complex banking operations, such as paying suppliers, treasury management, and investment banking services.

fields.name: Premium customers
fields.description: A user who pays for additional services and privileges, such as access to VIP lounges, concierge services, and personalized financial advice.

fields.name: Private Banking customers
fields.description: A high net worth individual who receives personalized and specialized services, such as portfolio management, tax planning, and investment advice.

fields.name: Stockbroker
fields.description: A high net worth individual who receives personalized and specialized services, such as portfolio management, tax planning, and investment advice.

fields.name: Financial Advisor
fields.description: A professional who buys and sells securities on behalf of the bank's clients.

fields.name: Account Manager
fields.description: A professional who manages relationships with the bank's clients and provides personalized and specialized services.

fields.name: Bank Employee
fields.description: A bank employee who has access to internal systems and data and performs administrative and operational tasks.

fields.name: System Administrator
fields.description: A professional who manages the bank's computer systems and telecommunications and ensures their operation and security.

fields.name: Auditor
fields.description: A professional who performs internal and external audits of the bank to ensure its regulatory compliance and financial integrity.

fields.name: Active
fields.description: The account is active and ready to perform operations.

fields.name: Inactive
fields.description: The account is inactive and cannot perform operations until it is reactivated.

fields.name: Blocked
fields.description: The account is temporarily blocked due to suspected fraud or suspicious activity.

fields.name: Frozen
fields.description: The account is frozen by court order or due to a dispute between the bank and the customer.

fields.name: Closed
fields.description: The account has been closed by the customer or the bank due to a violation of the terms and conditions.

fields.name: Under Review
fields.description: The account is being reviewed by the bank due to a request for information change or fraud investigation.

fields.name: On Hold
fields.description: The account is on hold for activation or reactivation after a customer request.

fields.name: Suspended
fields.description: The account is temporarily suspended due to non-payment or a violation of the terms and conditions.

fields.name: Dormant
fields.description: The account has been inactive for a prolonged period of time and is considered 'dormant'.

fields.name: In Opening Process
fields.description: The account is in the process of opening and is not yet ready for operations.

fields.name: In Closing Process
fields.description: The account is in the process of closing and cannot perform operations until the process is complete.

fields.name: Error
fields.description: The account has a technical or system error that prevents operations.

fields.name: Pending Verification
fields.description: The account is pending verification of the customer's identity or provided information.

fields.name: Limited
fields.description: The account has temporary or permanent limits for performing operations due to a customer request or bank decision.

fields.name: In Dispute
fields.description: The account is in dispute between the bank and the customer due to a transaction or service issue.

fields.name: Checking Account
fields.description: An account for performing daily operations, such as deposits, withdrawals, transfers, and bill payments.

fields.name: Savings Account
fields.description: An account for saving money and earning interest, with restrictions on frequent withdrawals.

fields.name: Investment Account
fields.description: An account for investing in financial assets, such as stocks, bonds, or mutual funds.

fields.name: Credit Account
fields.description: An account that allows the user to request loans or credit lines for financing purchases or projects.

fields.name: Payment Account
fields.description: An account for making online or in-person payments, such as a debit or credit account.

fields.name: Credit Card Account
fields.description: An account associated with a credit card, that allows the user to make purchases and payments online or in person.

fields.name: Time Deposit Account
fields.description: An account that allows the user to deposit money for a determined period of time and earn higher interest than a traditional savings account.

fields.name: Money Market Account
fields.description: An account that allows the user to invest in short-term financial instruments, such as certificates of deposit or bills of exchange.

fields.name: Retirement Account
fields.description: An account for saving for retirement, with tax benefits and restrictions on withdrawals before retirement age.

fields.name: Business Account
fields.description: An account for businesses and organizations, that allows for more complex banking operations, such as payments to suppliers and treasury management.

fields.name: Active
fields.description: The point of sale is active and ready to process sales.

fields.name: Inactive
fields.description: The point of sale is inactive and sales cannot be processed.

fields.name: Under Maintenance
fields.description: The point of sale is under maintenance and sales cannot be processed temporarily.

fields.name: Configuring
fields.description: The point of sale is being configured and sales cannot be processed until configuration is complete.

fields.name: Testing
fields.description: The point of sale is being tested to ensure it is functioning correctly.

fields.name: Disabled
fields.description: The point of sale has been disabled by the owner or administrator.

fields.name: Pending
fields.description: The point of sale is pending activation or reactivation after a request from the owner or administrator.

fields.name: Error
fields.description: The point of sale has a technical or system error that prevents sales from being processed.

fields.name: Updating
fields.description: The point of sale is being updated and sales cannot be processed until the update is complete.

fields.name: Closed
fields.description: The point of sale has been permanently closed and sales cannot be processed.

fields.name: Physical
fields.description: A physical point of sale, such as a store or a kiosk.

fields.name: Online
fields.description: An online point of sale, such as a virtual store or an e-commerce platform.

fields.name: Mobile
fields.description: A mobile point of sale, such as a mobile device or an app that allows sales to be made anywhere.

fields.name: Temporary
fields.description: A temporary point of sale, such as a stand at an event or a fair.

fields.name: Permanent
fields.description: A permanent point of sale, such as an established store in a fixed location.

fields.name: Active
fields.description: La tarjeta está activa y lista para ser utilizada.

fields.name: Inactive
fields.description: La tarjeta está inactiva y no se puede utilizar.

fields.name: Pending
fields.description: La tarjeta está pendiente de activación o reactivación después de una solicitud del titular.

fields.name: Blocked
fields.description: La tarjeta está bloqueada temporalmente debido a una sospecha de fraude o actividad sospechosa.

fields.name: Lost/Stolen
fields.description: La tarjeta ha sido reportada como perdida o robada y no se puede utilizar.

fields.name: Expired
fields.description: La tarjeta ha caducado y no se puede utilizar.

fields.name: Cancelled
fields.description: La tarjeta ha sido cancelada por el titular o el banco.

fields.name: Suspended
fields.description: La tarjeta está suspendida temporalmente debido a una falta de pago o actividad sospechosa.

fields.name: Under Review
fields.description: La tarjeta está siendo revisada por el banco debido a una sospecha de fraude o actividad sospechosa.

fields.name: Credit Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito que permite al titular realizar compras y pagar luego.

fields.name: Debit Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de débito que retira fondos directamente de la cuenta del titular.

fields.name: Prepaid Card
fields.description: Tarjeta prepaga que tiene un saldo predeterminado y se puede recargar.

fields.name: Virtual Card
fields.description: Tarjeta virtual que no tiene una forma física y se utiliza solo para transacciones en línea.

fields.name: Business Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito o débito para uso empresarial.

fields.name: Secured Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito que requiere un depósito de seguridad para garantizar el pago.

fields.name: Rewards Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito que ofrece recompensas o puntos por compras realizadas.

fields.name: Cashback Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito que ofrece un porcentaje de devolución de dinero por compras realizadas.

fields.name: Charge Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito que requiere que el titular pague el saldo completo cada mes.

fields.name: Student Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito diseñada específicamente para estudiantes.

fields.name: Travel Card
fields.description: Tarjeta de crédito o débito diseñada específicamente para viajes.

fields.name: Gift Card
fields.description: Tarjeta prepaga que se puede utilizar como regalo.
